      "bullets": [
        "Progressive JPEGs trigger multiple decode and paint cycles, causing CPU spikes and battery drain on modern high-speed networks.",
        "On fast connections, baseline JPEGs or modern formats like WebP and AVIF often deliver better Core Web Vitals performance.",
        "Optimize image pipelines by measuring decode costs; progressive encoding can degrade rendering efficiency on modern mobile browsers."
      ]
